column1: Compared to the previous week (launch week), there's been increase in total trials by ~6x from 1113 to 6514 in this week
There's been a increase in WoW spends as well by 9x from 1.9 lacs to 18.8 lacs
The most impacted metric in the funnel WoW has been the IR% that dropped from 23.5% to 14.8%
With the new shows in pipeline, we will be reducing our dependency on Saanwari and 31st
